{
  "id": "6a23ea22b1e5940bafc56cc2",
  "title": "虎哲",
  "created": 1780738596,
  "updated": 1780739625,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "6a23ea22b1e5940bafc56cc2",
      "text": "虎哲",
      "userId": "5f11a68e5fc065001ecf5795",
      "created": 1780738596,
      "updated": 1780738596
    },
    {
      "id": "6a23ea000000000000815bae",
      "text": " [希哲館]（希哲社）による[知機]の参考（リファレンス）実装[hiro.icon]",
      "userId": "5f11a68e5fc065001ecf5795",
      "created": 1780738596,
      "updated": 1780738643
    },
    {
      "id": "6a23ea300000000000815bb0",
      "text": "  読みは「こてつ」",
      "userId": "5f11a68e5fc065001ecf5795",
      "created": 1780738644,
      "updated": 1780738655
    },
    {
      "id": "6a23ea010000000000815baf",
      "text": "  名刀・長曽祢虎徹にちなむ",
      "userId": "5f11a68e5fc065001ecf5795",
      "created": 1780738596,
      "updated": 1780738937
    },
    {
      "id": "6a23eb560000000000815bb2",
      "text": "   もともと[希哲館]創立前から「[Dialektix]」という名前で構想していたものだった",
      "userId": "5f11a68e5fc065001ecf5795",
      "created": 1780738937,
      "updated": 1780739031
    },
    {
      "id": "6a23ebb40000000000815bb3",
      "text": "   [万軌]実装「[竜力]」とともに、希哲館と二大[相通化技術]であることを連想しやすいように調整していった",
      "userId": "5f11a68e5fc065001ecf5795",
      "created": 1780739031,
      "updated": 1780739235
    },
    {
      "id": "6a23ec7f0000000000815bb5",
      "text": "   イメージは知恵の剣、「知剣」である",
      "userId": "5f11a68e5fc065001ecf5795",
      "created": 1780739235,
      "updated": 1780739296
    },
    {
      "id": "6a23ec510000000000815bb4",
      "text": "    [仏教]でも煩悩を断ち切る智慧の剣という意味で「智剣」という表現が使われることがある",
      "userId": "5f11a68e5fc065001ecf5795",
      "created": 1780739188,
      "updated": 1780739410
    },
    {
      "id": "6a23ecce0000000000815bb6",
      "text": "    虎哲はどちらかというと煩悩を極めて涅槃を切り裂く剣である",
      "userId": "5f11a68e5fc065001ecf5795",
      "created": 1780739314,
      "updated": 1780739477
    },
    {
      "id": "6a23edfc0000000000815bb8",
      "text": "  [デライト]は虎哲の部分実装にあたる",
      "userId": "5f11a68e5fc065001ecf5795",
      "created": 1780739616,
      "updated": 1780739625
    },
    {
      "id": "6a23ed3d0000000000815bb7",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5f11a68e5fc065001ecf5795",
      "created": 1780739426,
      "updated": 1780739426
    }
  ]
}